snippet.title: The Last Flower Trailer
snippet.description:
The Last Flower follows Sara's quest in search of a mystical flower, said to bring people back from the dead.

With a goal in mind, this warrior won't stop at anything to make it come true.

-itch.io link: https://marron121.itch.io/the-last-flower
